name: Frog Jump - Tap !
description:
"Frog" - colorful and fun game for children in which the frog has to jump from leaf to leaf, and not fall into the water. Your task is to go as far as possible! Children’s game "Frog" will not let you get bored and will provide an opportunity to test your reaction. Bright design, lively music and a cute frog is very pleasant to children.
Join the adventure in which the frog will pass its way!
